04:49.056 --> 04:50.522
"Overjoyed to learn

04:50.524 --> 04:52.057
"of Adam's emancipation.
Mazel Tov to you both.

04:52.059 --> 04:53.392
Wish I could be there."

04:53.394 --> 04:54.526
Oh. Where is Max anyway?

04:54.528 --> 04:56.495
STEVE:
He's overseas.

04:56.496 --> 04:58.463
He's doing a little bit of work
for Doctors Without Borders.

04:58.465 --> 04:59.865
No kidding. Yeah. (phone rings)

04:59.867 --> 05:01.300
Excuse me.

05:01.302 --> 05:03.635
KONO:
Oh, this one's

05:03.637 --> 05:06.038
