Uh-oh.

05:06.040 --> 05:08.006
"Hey, Spicy. Hear
your hubby's out.

05:08.008 --> 05:09.775
Congrats. Tell him..."

05:09.777 --> 05:10.909
Mm-hmm.
That's disgusting.

05:10.911 --> 05:12.477
I can't even read this out loud.

05:12.479 --> 05:14.846
